'''Ostrine''' was a mineral found on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Hargeeva]]. It had the property of absorbing great amounts of heat, lending to its use in armor plating for [[Stormtrooper/Legends|stormtroopers]] and other Imperial soldiers. It was also once used to make blades for melee weapons during the [[Dark Wars]]. Its properties were multiplied by ten-fold when [[Ketrian Altronel]] discovered that crystalline manipulation and [[plas-bonding]] of certain trace elements modified it, resulting in the mineral being able to freeze objects instantaneously that came in contact with it.

Defecting to the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]], Altronel would help increase the firepower of [[T-65 X-wing starfighter/Legends|T-65 X-wing starfighters]] by adding the formula to the housings of its [[Laser cannon/Legends|laser cannons]].

